data.description: Spectacular Custom 3br 2ba home built in 2019.This home offers a delightful open concept floorplan, 2LR,Ranch style Kit with beautiful stone accent island with sink and breakfast bar that complements the chosen slate stone floors throughout the home.Split bedrooms,Mstr complete with en-suite bath and HUGE walk in closet.Plenty windows allow an abundance of natural light along with a custom neutral color that adorns the walls certain to accent any decor beautifully.Located in town on large corner lot with privacy fence,storage building and two of the most beautiful full mature pecan trees in the neighborhood. Have a garden,build a shop or put in a pool. This home HAS ROOM FOR IT ALL.   No SIY at sellers request.
